'''Sagiyama Kofun''' (鷺山古墳) is a {{ill|kofun|ja|古墳|1=Kofun|qq=draft|qq=draft}} located in {{ill|Kokufu Town, Tottori City|ja|鳥取市国府町|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Tottori Prefecture|ja|鳥取県|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. Its shape is a circular tomb (円墳). The kofun is designated as a historic site by Tottori Prefecture.
